creator: T3 Technologies
descriptionHtml:
Coachbox Mobile compliments our Coachbox web platform and centralizes our most used features for your pocket-size devices.

Coachbox is used by endurance coaches, athletes, clubs and teams of many sports around the world, including running, cycling, swimming, triathlon, … and helps you win time to plan, analyze and communicate with your peers.

• Quickly check your calendar and view your workouts on the go
• Plan and edit events and races
• Give feedback and send notifications
• Analyze logged activities and check progress towards predefined goals
